defaultBut introducing a measure of progress
default would recognise the severe and hazardous journey many young people have travelled, the efforts of those who have helped them, as well as more understanding of the complex roots and reasons for their vulnerability.  It may also provide a more sophisticated
default way of identifying problems experienced by young people and a focus for intervention
default which may well
default contribute to improving normative outcomes, over time.
